country: To address the challenge of inconsistent yearly observations from different countries, we created decadal averages from available data from 2000 to 2013 to derive single summary values of wastewater treatment and connection rate. If there were no values available for a country for 2000 to 2013, we used an average of available values for 1990 to 2000 to represent the summary wastewater treatment or connection rate value of that country.
The order of preference when merging datasets was: 1) OECD (2013); 2) the United Nations Statistics Division (UNSD, 2011); 3) Pinsent-Masons (2011); and 4) the FAO Aquastat database
